race.description: Tab Federal Road To The Chest
race.comment: An open contest. VERMICELLA (9) brings strong form and resumes after 79 days with a tick over trial. She's right up to this at best and has won 2/3 first up. Maps for a soft run and Mathew Cahill is a key jockey engagement. The betting will be key. Ditto with MOUNTAIN CHATTER (8), who resumes and has switched to the Nick Olive yard. He also performs fresh and brings compelling form from the back of his previous preparation. He draws wide, but an in-form rider is booked. CHAMPIONS LEAGUE (7) has threatened this level/track both starts this preparation. He will need the pace on, but rates well and will be hitting the line hard. FANGELA (2) is third-up and has a handy 2kg claim. He will be around the mark putting his best foot forward.
